            . I am mate of a brig, which was laying in the <placeName id="t18310908-403-crimeloc2074">Export-dock, Poplar</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18310908-403-crimeloc2074" type="placeName" value="Export-dock, Poplar"></interp>
